item.title: A Feeling I Can't Shake
item.description: I have almost everything anyone could ask for, but my emotions and mental state don't reflect that. Why? That's the question that's been killing me for the past couple of months. The past few months have thrown me a ton of curveballs. I moved out of San Francisco and back into my parents place. On one hand, it's been awesome to chill with them and my sister. On the other hand, my days have become more and more routine.
